      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HOLLY MAGIC (1) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (21.97) at this track behind Colonel's Dream in a Grade 4/5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Has a solid record from this box including two wins and a minor placing. Capable of going well again. ASCEND KALMIA (2) finished third (29.37) two back at this track but out of the placings last time when 8th there. Cannot be taken lightly. HE PLAYED ONE (5) has a moderate overall strike-rate. Better run when finding the frame last time though, finishing second (29.26) at this track. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Will give a great sight again. DON'T TELL SHILO (7) gets a chance to improve on an unplaced run at her latest outing at this circuit.",
